fields.description: Tiny black flies that do not hurt Isaac upon touch.
Red Flies that follow Isaac and deal touch damage.
Follows Isaac, similar to Attack Flies. Will split into 2 Attack Flies upon death.
fields.Eternal: Splits into 4 Attack Flies instead of 2.

fields.description: Invulnerable Fly that circles Corny Poop, Holy Leeches or Hangers.
Slow-moving flies that fire single blood shots at Isaac. Pooters do not deal contact damage.
fields.Eternal: Fires 3 shots in quick succession.

fields.description: Alternate version of Pooters. Fires 2 shots in a V-formation and does not deal contact damage.
fields.Eternal: Fires 3 sets of 3 shots in a V-formation.

fields.description: Flies around the room diagonally, dealing touch damage and exploding with a large blast radius upon death.
fields.Eternal: Explodes with very large blast radius upon death.

fields.description: Flies around the room diagonally, dealing touch damage and exploding into 6 directional blood shots upon death.
fields.Eternal: Explodes into a dense ring of blood shots upon death.

fields.description: Flies slowly towards Isaac, exploding into 4 projectiles in a + formation upon death.
fields.Eternal: Shoots 4 projectiles in a + formation, exploding into 8 blood shots upon death.

fields.description: Flies slowly towards Isaac, exploding into an IPECAC shot upon death which targets other Spits in the room, or Isaac.
fields.Eternal: Shoots 4 projectiles diagonally, exploding into 3 IPECAC shots upon death.

fields.description: Moves erratically around the room, damaging Isaac by touch.
Moves erratically around the room, splitting into two Spiders upon death.
fields.Eternal: Explodes into many Spiders upon death.

fields.description: Quickly jumps towards Isaac with high distance. If Isaac is too far away it will jump around randomly.
fields.Eternal: Leaves slowing creep and shoots 4 projectiles in a + formation wherever it lands.

fields.description: Stationary enemy that shrinks upon being hit. Will quickly swell up if not killed in time. Fires multiple short-ranged blood projectiles when fully swollen.
fields.Eternal: Fires a larger volley of blood projectiles.

fields.description: Stationary enemy that shrinks upon being hit. Will quickly swell up if not killed in time. Fires an IPECAC shot when fully swollen.
fields.Eternal: Fires 3 IPECAC shots instead of one.

fields.description: Stationary enemy that shrinks upon being hit. Swells up slower than Guts and Boils. Spawns a Spider when fully swollen.
fields.Eternal: Spawns two Spiders instead of one.

fields.description: Mobile Boil that cannot shrink, but has a finite amount of health. Fires short-ranged blood shots with varying sizes at a reduced fire rate.
fields.Eternal: Fires a larger volley of blood projectiles.

fields.description: Mobile Gut that cannot shrink, but has a finite amount of health. Fires IPECAC shots at a reduced fire rate.
fields.Eternal: Fires 3 IPECAC shots instead of one.

fields.description: Mobile Sack that cannot shrink, but has a finite amount of health. Spawns Spiders.
fields.Eternal: Spawns two Spiders instead of one.

fields.description: Harmless enemy that walks around the room, avoiding Isaac. Will spawn multiple flies upon death.
fields.Eternal: Periodically fires 4 shots in a + formation whenever Isaac is standing to that formation.

fields.description: Harmless enemy that walks around the room, avoiding Isaac. Will drop a Troll Bomb upon death.
fields.Eternal: Periodically spawns Spiders while running away.

fields.description: Walks towards Isaac, exploding with a large blast radius upon death or upon touching Isaac. The explosion does a half-heart of damage instead of the regular full heart.
fields.Eternal: Continuously fires two IPECAC shots while walking.

fields.description: Walks around the room, avoiding Isaac while spawning Attack Flies. Spawns a large number of Flies upon death.
fields.Eternal: Spawns two flies instead of one each time, and spawns more flies upon death. Can sometimes be a mini-boss with health bar and larger body, spitting eternal flies and has orbital eternal flies.

fields.description: Slowly floats around the room, spawning a Pooter upon taking damage. Spawns a large number of Flies upon death.
fields.Eternal: Spawns Eternal Flies instead of regular Flies, one Pooter and one Eternal Fly when damaged, and will split into 3 non-Eternal Swarmers when killed.

fields.description: Jumps around the room slowly, damaging Isaac by touch.
fields.Eternal: Stands still before start pursuing Isaac, firing 4 blood projectiles in a + formation after it lands.

fields.description: Jumps around the room quickly, covering a large distance, similar to Trites.
fields.Eternal: Stands still before start pursuing Isaac, firing 4 blood projectiles in a + formation after it lands.

fields.description: Jumps around the room quickly, but not as fast as F. Hoppers. Occasionally jumps high into the air, dropping down elsewhere while firing 4 blood shots in a plus pattern.
fields.Eternal: Stands still before start pursuing Isaac, firing 4 blood projectiles in a + formation after it lands, and 8 blood shots in all directions after the big jump.

fields.description: Walks aimlessly around the room. Usually spawned after killing a Gaper/Frowning Gaper.
Walks aimlessly around the room, firing extremely short-ranged blood projectiles from its head. Usually spawned after killing a Gaper/Frowning Gaper.
fields.Eternal: Walks towards Isaac, firing fast projectiles in Isaac's general direction.

fields.description: Walks towards Isaac, dealing contact damage. Usually turns into a Pacer or Gusher upon death.
fields.Eternal: Always turns into an Eternal Gusher or Eternal Horf upon death.

fields.description: Walks towards Isaac, dealing contact damage. If Isaac is in sight, its eyes will open and it will walk faster. Usually turns into a Pacer or Gusher upon death.
fields.Eternal: Always turns into an Eternal Gusher or Eternal Horf upon death.

fields.description: Slowly walks towards Isaac, firing short-ranged IPECAC shots at him. Has much more health than regular Gapers.
fields.Eternal: Leaves a trail of damaging creep and fires a long-ranged homing IPECAC shot at Isaac.

fields.description: Walks towards Isaac, quickly launching its head, still attached to its body by a cord. Turns into a Maw or Pacer upon death.
fields.Eternal: Shoots 8 shots in all directions every time it shoots its head.

fields.description: Stationary enemy that fires medium ranged blood shots at Isaac.
fields.Eternal: Shoots a wide spread of 5 blood shots each time.

fields.description: Floats towards Isaac, firing fast-moving blood shots.
fields.Eternal: Fires spread volleys of 9 blood projectiles.

fields.description: Floats towards Isaac faster than regular Maws, exploding into 4 blood shots in a plus pattern upon death. Does not fire any shots.
fields.Eternal: Constantly leaves red creep and explodes into 8 shots in all directions upon death.

fields.description: Alternate version of a Maw, has an Eternal Fly circling it. Fires large, purple homing shots at Isaac.
fields.Eternal: 3 Eternal Flies instead of one.

fields.description: Walks towards Isaac, dealing one heart of contact damage. Turns into a pile of goo after taking enough damage, where it can be killed. Will regenerate after a short amount of time if not killed quickly.
fields.Eternal: Fires a ring of 8 blood projectiles after collapsing into a pile of goo.

fields.description: Quickly walks towards Isaac, dealing one heart of contact damage. Turns into a pile of goo and slides away after taking enough damage, where it can be killed. Will regenerate after a short amount of time if not killed quickly.
fields.Eternal: Fires a ring of 8 blood projectiles after collapsing into a pile of goo, also keeping firing while slide away.

fields.description: Moves erratically around the room. Can only be damaged from behind.
fields.Eternal: Reflects Isaac's shots on its face and leaves red creep each time it takes damage.

fields.description: Moves erratically around the room, charging at Isaac at very high speed. Can only be damaged from behind.
fields.Eternal: Reflects Isaac's shots on its face and leaves red creep each time it takes damage.

fields.description: Invulnerable mask with a slow-moving Heart. Functions similarly to a Knight. The Heart fires 4 blood shots in a plus pattern when Isaac gets near. Killing the Heart will automatically kill the Mask.
fields.Eternal: Eternal Heart fires 8 shots in all directions in quick succession, shooting 4 shots in the cardinal directions upon death. Eternal Mask immediately teleport back to the corresponding Heart and start charging should the Heart take damage.

fields.description: Moves around the room, firing 4 blood shots in a + pattern.
fields.Eternal: Fires 3 sets of 4 blood projectiles in a + pattern as well as multiple various-sized blood projectiles in random directions.

fields.description: Moves around the room, firing 4 tar shots in an X pattern.
fields.Eternal: Fires 3 sets of 4 blood projectiles in an X pattern as well as multiple various-sized blood projectiles in random directions.

fields.description: Moves around the room, firing 8 shots in all directions.
fields.Eternal: Fires 3 sets of 8 blood projectiles in all directions as well as multiple various-sized blood projectiles in random directions while also slowly move toward Isaac.

fields.description: Aimlessly moves around the room, damaging Isaac by contact.
fields.Eternal: Leaves green creep, and after a few seconds, it will transform into an Eternal Sack, which will in turn after a few seconds transform into an Eternal Fat Fly.

fields.description: Slowly moves around the room, charging at Isaac when he gets in its line of sight.
fields.Eternal: Leaves green creep, and after a few seconds, it will transform into an Eternal Sack, which will in turn after a few seconds transform into an Eternal Fat Fly.

fields.description: Slowly moves around the room, firing a single long-ranged blood shot when Isaac gets in its line of sight.
fields.Eternal: Fires 3 projectiles, one in the center and two in a V-formation when Isaac gets in its line of sight.

fields.description: Crawls around the room, leaving a trail of red Creep that does one heart of damage.
fields.Eternal: Shoots a homing blood shot at Isaac.

fields.description: Slowly moves around the room, occasionally hopping and firing 8 large blood shots in all directions. Will split into 2 Brains upon death.
fields.Eternal: Shoots 8 homing blood shots and spawns 3-4 Eternal Brains upon death.

fields.description: Attaches itself to a wall or obstacle, such as a Rock, rolling around the room.
fields.Eternal: Moves faster and occasionally shoots 8 shots in all directions.

fields.description: Slowly moves around the room, occasionally hopping and firing 8 large blood shots in all directions. Will split into 2 Guts upon death.
fields.Eternal: Fires 8 large blood shots in quick succession and spawns 2 Eternal Guts and 1 Eternal Clotty upon death.

fields.description: Attaches itself to other B. Lickers, erratically moving around the room, similar to Larry Jr.
fields.Eternal: Starts pursuing Isaac, leaving behind red creep.

fields.description: Moves towards Isaac. Can burrow underground and reappear elsewhere.
fields.Eternal: Stops pursuing Isaac, spawning 3 smaller Eternal Para-Bites that is close to him.

fields.description: Fires an IPECAC shot at Isaac. Will hop out of the ground and burrow elsewhere, firing 4 blood shots in an X pattern while doing so.
fields.Eternal: Fires a homing IPECAC shot at Isaac, leaving 8 shots in all directions when diving into ground.

fields.description: Fires 3 fast-moving blood shots at Isaac when he gets in its line of sight. Will burrow underground and reappear elsewhere after firing its shots.
fields.Eternal: Fires 3 blood shots in quick succession.

fields.description: Quickly charges towards Isaac when he gets in its line of sight.
Quickly charges towards Isaac when he gets in its line of sight. Explodes with a large blast radius upon death.
fields.Eternal: Shoots continuous shots to both sides while moving and has an Eternal Fly circling it.

fields.description: Quickly charges towards Isaac when he gets in its line of sight. Explodes with a large blast radius upon death. Has an Eternal Fly circling it.
fields.Eternal: Shoots continuous shots to both sides while moving.

fields.description: Invulnerable stationary enemy. Raises its head up when Isaac gets close, revealing a fleshy stem that can be damaged. Upon raising its head, it will fire 3 blood shots and lower its head again.
fields.Eternal: Invulnerable stationary enemy that reflects Isaac's tears. Raises its head up when Isaac gets close, revealing a fleshy stem that can be damaged. Upon raising its head, it will either fire 5 blood shots in a V formation and lower its head again, or quickly lower its head and fire 8 shots around it.

fields.description: Stationary enemy that can be damaged even when its head is lowered. Fires 5 blood shots instead of 3 when rising, and fires more frequently.
fields.Eternal: Fires 7 blood shots in quick succession. Sometimes, it quickly lower its head and fire 8 shots around it.

fields.description: Charges up a Brimstone laser when Isaac gets in its line of sight.
Charges up a Brimstone laser which fires from both sides when Isaac gets in its line of sight.
fields.Eternal: Leaves red creep each time it fires a Brimstone laser.

fields.description: Fires a Little Chubby-like familiar that deals one heart of damage when Isaac gets in its line of sight.
fields.Eternal: Leaves red creep each time it shoots a Charger.

fields.description: Moves around the room, damaging Isaac by contact.
Quickly slides towards Isaac when he gets in front of it.
Quickly fires a Technology-like laser at Isaac.
fields.Eternal: Occasionally shoot continuous blood shots. When this happens, it will keep spinning until it stops after a few seconds.

fields.description: Quickly fires a Brimstone-like laser at Isaac.
Copies Isaac's movements, and fires tears at the same time as him.
Copies Isaac's movements, and fires tears at the same time as him.
Aimlessly hops around the room, damaging Isaac by contact damage.
fields.Eternal: Shoots large rings of blood shots every time it jumps. Upon taking enough damage, it splits into 4 smaller Eternal Embryos that shoot less blood shots. Smaller Eternal Embryos, however, can only split into 2 even smaller ones, and they no longer shoot blood shots if they are smaller than half-sized ones.

fields.description: Fires a single blood shot at Isaac. Can teleport and reappear elsewhere.
fields.Eternal: Leaves 4 blood shots in a + pattern when teleporting.

fields.description: Fires 3 blood shots at once at Isaac, has much more health than regular Babies.
fields.Eternal: Leaves 8 blood shots in all directions when teleporting.

fields.description: Hops around the room, firing 2 blood shots in a V formation at Isaac.
fields.Eternal: Stands still before start pursuing Isaac, firing 4 shots each time it lands and also fires 2 shots in quick succession at Isaac.

fields.description: Floats around the room, firing 3 blood shots at Isaac. Has an Eternal Fly circling it.
fields.Eternal: Fires 3 homing blood shots at Isaac.

fields.description: Stationary and invulnerable monster that fires a fast-moving blood shot at Isaac. Stops firing when room is cleared.
Stationary and invulnerable monster that fires an IPECAC shot at Isaac. Stops firing when room is cleared.
